T1  - Citizenship Behavior and Social Exchange
AU  - Konovsky, Mary A.
AU  - Pugh, S. Douglas
Y1  - 1994/06/01
PY  - 1994
DA  - 1994/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256704
